WEBVTT

00:05.089 --> 00:07.591
WHILE THIS STORY IS BASED
ON ACTUAL EVENTS,

00:07.675 --> 00:11.345
CERTAIN CHARACTERS, INCIDENTS,
AND DIALOGUE WERE FICTIONALIZED.

00:11.429 --> 00:14.974
ANY SIMILARITY TO ANY PERSON,
IS FOR DRAMATIC PURPOSES.

00:41.792 --> 00:45.796
I have to remind you that
you can only answer yes or no.

00:47.631 --> 00:49.800
Is your name Cristiana Sinagra?

00:49.884 --> 00:50.801
Yes.

01:48.025 --> 01:50.653
MARADONA:
BLESSED DREAM

01:56.033 --> 02:01.038
NAPLES, ITALY.

03:33.088 --> 03:33.964
Coming!

03:42.598 --> 03:44.099
What are you doing here?

03:44.975 --> 03:47.269
You invited me to dinner. Wasn't it today?

03:47.436 --> 03:50.147
What are you wearing? What did you bring?

03:51.231 --> 03:52.775
I'm not letting you in.

03:53.275 --> 03:54.526
Then I'm leaving.

03:55.194 --> 03:56.362
Come on in.

04:07.957 --> 04:09.875
-What a beautiful house.
-Thanks.

04:10.709 --> 04:12.086
Take that jacket off.

04:31.689 --> 04:33.357
Is your father very jealous?

04:33.440 --> 04:35.442
Maybe we should hide his scissors.

04:35.526 --> 04:39.571
My dad works as a hairdresser, he can
give you a haircut with those scissors.

04:39.655 --> 04:43.534
Anyways, I am going to take a shower.
You can finish here.

04:43.617 --> 04:46.245
-Me?
-Why, are you not able to?

04:46.328 --> 04:48.956
What do you think? I come from nothing.

04:49.289 --> 04:51.750
I was born in a neighborhood
poorer than this one.

04:51.834 --> 04:55.254
My mother would fake having a tummy ache
so we could eat.

04:55.337 --> 04:57.881
Sure, sure. Come on now, Maradó.

04:58.465 --> 05:01.552
Maradó, Maradó, these folks are crazy.

05:01.760 --> 05:03.637
They think I can't mop a floor.

05:14.398 --> 05:15.315
Try it.

05:17.985 --> 05:19.028
Is it tasty?

05:26.994 --> 05:29.580
I think we should find a good pizzeria...

05:30.039 --> 05:33.792
Baby, I prepare a dreamy ragou.

05:35.627 --> 05:38.005
I'm kidding. It's amazing.

05:47.765 --> 05:49.475
And you're a good kisser too.

05:52.269 --> 05:54.188
What about your engagement?

05:56.148 --> 05:58.400
It's a long, long story,

05:58.484 --> 06:02.154
but I am in love like the first day.

06:04.573 --> 06:07.201
I know that
there is no other woman like her,

06:09.078 --> 06:12.456
nobody whom I'll love more.

06:13.082 --> 06:14.708
But... Wasn't it over?

06:15.959 --> 06:17.836
It will never be over.

06:19.004 --> 06:20.089
What do you mean?

06:21.173 --> 06:24.301
Because... I won't leave Tota.

06:24.510 --> 06:26.553
-Your mother!
-Yes, my mom.

06:32.851 --> 06:34.853
Your dad is giving me a mean look.

06:37.106 --> 06:38.273
Sorry, Dad.

06:50.369 --> 06:51.245
You're tense.

06:52.913 --> 06:53.831
I'm scared.

06:54.456 --> 06:55.374
Scared of what?

06:57.292 --> 07:00.671
They say you are a womanizer.
That you take drugs.

07:01.296 --> 07:03.715
And that you are involved in the Camorra.

07:05.926 --> 07:07.094
What do you think?

07:09.304 --> 07:14.059
Do I seem like a mobster,
drug addict, womanizer?

07:32.077 --> 07:33.495
<i>San Paolo Stadium in Naples.</i>

07:33.579 --> 07:37.875
<i>Playing today Salvatore Bagni,</i>
<i>Moreno Ferrario, Alessandro Renica,</i>

07:37.958 --> 07:42.212
<i>Eraldo Pecci, Bruno Giordano,</i>
<i>Luigi Capparelli, Costanzo Celestini</i>

07:42.296 --> 07:45.591
<i>and, of course, the captain</i>
<i>Diego Armando Maradona.</i>

07:45.674 --> 07:50.220
<i>Maradona is struggling,</i>
<i>he is touching his knee.</i>

07:50.304 --> 07:53.223
<i>We see him in pain</i>
<i>in the middle of the field.</i>

08:01.899 --> 08:04.151
We don't think he can play,

08:04.318 --> 08:08.363
but doctor Oliva wants
to go ahead with the infiltrations.

08:08.822 --> 08:11.992
Dr. Oliva, we won't allow him
to play anesthetized.

08:12.075 --> 08:14.494
Excuse me,
I don't think Diego needs surgery.

08:14.912 --> 08:16.788
It's the muscle, not the bone.

08:16.914 --> 08:19.666
That's how they break permanently.

08:19.791 --> 08:20.667
I disagree.

08:20.792 --> 08:23.420
Thank you, but the club has the final say.

08:23.503 --> 08:26.715
What about me? Only Maradona decides
about Maradona's body.

08:26.798 --> 08:28.717
Wrong. Your contract with Napoli...

08:28.800 --> 08:31.678
Contract? I wipe my ass
with your contract, Ferlaino!

08:31.762 --> 08:33.555
Dr. Oliva is an eminence,

08:33.639 --> 08:35.933
he can teach the job to every one of you.

08:50.697 --> 08:52.574
<i>Napoli starts playing.</i>

08:53.283 --> 08:56.411
<i>We see Diego Maradona</i>
<i>with the ball between his feet.</i>

08:56.745 --> 08:59.248
<i>We see him hurt. And...</i>

08:59.373 --> 09:05.295
Foul on Diego Maradona.
They get him out in a stretcher.

09:10.842 --> 09:12.970
I broke it, it cracked.

09:13.136 --> 09:16.473
Don't worry, it's what I told you,
it's detached now.

09:18.350 --> 09:19.559
Let's do another shot.

09:22.980 --> 09:25.315
Come. Cover me, I'll give him a shot.

09:33.156 --> 09:37.202
Move it for a few minutes,
even if it hurts, and go out on the field.

09:37.828 --> 09:42.291
Diego! Diego!

09:42.874 --> 09:44.376
Trust me, you'll be fine.

09:51.925 --> 09:55.470
<i>Even with his injury,</i>
<i>he dodges the other players.</i>

09:56.388 --> 09:59.266
<i>He gets the ball, closes in on the goal,</i>
<i>left and...</i>

09:59.349 --> 10:03.061
<i>Goal, goal!</i>
<i>Goal from the Napoli captain!</i>

10:03.186 --> 10:05.272
<i>The public rejoices.</i>

10:05.355 --> 10:09.067
<i>The team members</i>
<i>want to hug their captain.</i>

10:09.693 --> 10:13.488
So where are the people who wanted
to send me for surgery now?

10:40.057 --> 10:43.352
That's enough, boys.

10:43.435 --> 10:46.772
<i>Oh, Mom, Mom, Mom</i>

10:46.855 --> 10:49.983
<i>You know why my heart beats?</i>

10:50.108 --> 10:53.904
<i>Because I saw Maradona, I saw Maradona</i>

10:54.029 --> 10:56.073
<i>Hey, Mom</i>

10:56.156 --> 10:58.575
Very nice, very nice.

10:58.658 --> 11:01.328
We'll meet some other time.

11:01.411 --> 11:04.373
He needs to sleep now,
he has practice in the morning.

11:04.456 --> 11:08.627
Some<i> ragazzas</i> are waiting for us
in the car. They're twins.

11:09.336 --> 11:10.962
-Party.
-Where did you find them?

11:11.046 --> 11:14.758
They were waiting in line
for an autograph.

11:14.841 --> 11:15.842
Hi.

11:15.967 --> 11:20.514
I approached them,
did my magic and left them...

11:21.681 --> 11:23.058
Ready for love.

11:24.184 --> 11:25.560
-Get it?
-Yes.

11:25.811 --> 11:27.604
-Yes.
-Did Rengo do this for you?

11:27.687 --> 11:28.563
No, he didn't.

11:29.147 --> 11:33.068
Besides, I got some good stuff
that gets you hard.

11:33.276 --> 11:34.444
-No way.
-It's true!

11:34.820 --> 11:35.904
I'd like to see that.

11:36.613 --> 11:37.447
Girls.

11:39.449 --> 11:41.243
Diego Armando Maradona.

11:41.368 --> 11:42.619
Hi, boy.

11:44.413 --> 11:45.872
-Alegra.
-How are you?

11:46.039 --> 11:47.165
-What's up?
-Love you.

11:47.249 --> 11:48.417
And I love you.

11:48.542 --> 11:50.919
-Yes.
-They are so beautiful.

11:51.044 --> 11:53.296
-Are you sure we won't go to jail?
-No.

11:53.380 --> 11:56.216
They'll be legal this year,
or the next one.

11:57.134 --> 11:58.802
All good, all legal, Diego.

12:11.731 --> 12:13.817
-It's wrong...
-It's ringing.

12:14.943 --> 12:15.819
Right.

12:15.986 --> 12:18.280
It's a cordless phone.

12:18.697 --> 12:21.867
To talk in the streets.
"Hello?" in the streets.

12:21.992 --> 12:24.578
Hello wherever you want. It's cordless.

12:24.661 --> 12:25.537
Yes.

12:25.620 --> 12:28.540
I'm still not used to it. Sorry.

12:29.040 --> 12:29.958
Hello?

12:31.251 --> 12:32.461
What's up? How are you?

12:32.544 --> 12:34.254
Worried about your knee.

12:35.088 --> 12:36.923
I almost died when you fell.

12:37.007 --> 12:40.719
I was scared too, but now I feel great.
It's okay now.

12:40.844 --> 12:43.763
What are you doing now?
Did you leave the stadium?

12:45.932 --> 12:50.645
I'm leaving with Guillermo.
We'll eat something and then home. You?

12:50.729 --> 12:51.771
I'm alone.

12:53.899 --> 12:55.358
Why don't you come here?

12:56.151 --> 12:57.068
I miss you.

12:57.944 --> 13:02.699
I miss you too,
but I have already made plans with him.

13:02.908 --> 13:04.201
<i>No problem, sweetheart.</i>

13:05.368 --> 13:06.453
See you tomorrow?

13:06.536 --> 13:07.704
<i>I can't tomorrow.</i>

13:07.829 --> 13:10.290
I'm going to Rome.
I'll be back on Saturday.

13:10.373 --> 13:12.501
<i>A week without seeing you?</i>

13:14.794 --> 13:16.213
I'm coming over now.

13:16.546 --> 13:17.589
Really?

13:18.089 --> 13:20.884
What about Guillermo?
Are you bringing him too?

13:21.301 --> 13:24.137
Don't worry,
he'll find himself something to do.

13:24.221 --> 13:27.766
Okay, I'll wait for you, my love. Bye.

13:34.147 --> 13:36.900
What's the matter, love? Are you sad?

13:38.818 --> 13:40.362
Everyone in Naples is sad.

13:43.156 --> 13:45.909
It was on the news today
that he's out of danger.

13:46.117 --> 13:47.494
Yeah, I know.

13:48.620 --> 13:51.498
There's people standing
outside the hospital for days.

13:51.665 --> 13:55.168
They write him letters,
pray for him, support him.

13:56.294 --> 13:58.171
I could write him a letter too.

13:59.089 --> 14:00.966
Of course you can write to him.

14:02.342 --> 14:05.220
Maybe now that he's almost dead,
he can read it.

14:06.096 --> 14:06.930
<i>Yes.</i>

14:07.764 --> 14:09.641
He might even answer this time.

14:09.724 --> 14:11.977
This time I'm sure he'll reply to you.

14:17.148 --> 14:18.650
<i>Diego is mine. Take Pelé.</i>

14:19.568 --> 14:21.987
<i>Who cares? Pelé is better than Maradona!</i>

14:22.404 --> 14:24.114
<i>Shut up! That's not true!</i>

14:24.239 --> 14:25.282
Diego, enough.

14:25.657 --> 14:28.868
Keep your voice down.
I have an important call to make.

14:42.799 --> 14:43.758
Sinagra.

14:44.009 --> 14:47.262
-She must want to know how Diego is.
-I'll get rid of her.

14:47.387 --> 14:49.055
Strange she didn't call earlier.

14:50.390 --> 14:51.224
Hi, Cristiana.

14:51.308 --> 14:54.728
-Hi, Claudia, how are you?
<i>-Trying not to give up.</i>

14:55.812 --> 14:58.106
<i>Is there a problem</i>
<i>with your son's allowance?</i>

14:58.481 --> 15:01.109
I had to delegate
everything to an accountant.

15:01.651 --> 15:03.778
I'm a little busy, as you can imagine.

15:03.945 --> 15:06.489
Of course,
I just want to know how Diego is.

15:06.698 --> 15:08.450
Better. Still under observation.

15:09.075 --> 15:12.787
Not sure if there'll be after-effects,
but the worst part is over.

15:13.038 --> 15:14.039
<i>Thank God.</i>

15:14.998 --> 15:17.709
How are you? How are the girls?

15:17.792 --> 15:18.960
Scared, obviously.

15:19.919 --> 15:21.796
Claudia, I don't want to impose.

15:23.423 --> 15:26.426
My son is very concerned
about his father's health.

15:26.635 --> 15:30.221
It would comfort him to hear his voice.
Even if just once.

15:31.348 --> 15:33.600
Cristiana, I swear I understand you.

15:34.517 --> 15:38.021
Diego never wanted to talk to your son,
and that won't change.

15:38.104 --> 15:41.441
Claudia, please.
From one mother to another.

15:42.609 --> 15:44.486
<i>It's hard to see a child in pain.</i>

15:44.611 --> 15:47.530
Diego rejects you, Cristiana,
what should I do?

15:47.614 --> 15:49.949
Why am I to blame for your relationship?

15:50.909 --> 15:54.788
Okay, Claudia. I'm sorry.
You're absolutely right.

15:57.540 --> 16:01.211
I'm sorry, I'm a little overwhelmed.
Forgive me.

16:02.045 --> 16:05.465
<i>Could my son write a letter to Diego?</i>

16:05.548 --> 16:08.677
If I send it to your email,
could you show it to him?

16:09.427 --> 16:12.681
Okay, I will try to get him to read it.
But no promises.

16:13.890 --> 16:15.600
<i>Okay, Claudia. Thanks.</i>

16:27.570 --> 16:30.323
She wants the boy
to write a letter to Diego.

16:31.616 --> 16:34.619
As if Diego cared about anyone.

16:38.081 --> 16:39.916
His only concern is himself.

16:39.999 --> 16:41.334
-No, Claudia, stop.
-What?

16:41.418 --> 16:43.628
-He cares about his daughters.
-Sure, yes.

16:43.712 --> 16:45.588
Dalma and Giannina, sure.

16:46.214 --> 16:49.676
He always talks about them,
and then he does this.

16:49.759 --> 16:54.639
-He overdoses. He's there, in a bed.
-He can't control it.

16:55.223 --> 16:56.641
And if he kills himself?

16:57.934 --> 17:01.020
How many kids
does Diego have in the world?

17:01.521 --> 17:05.817
He has slept with every woman he met.
He doesn't like to wear condoms.

17:05.900 --> 17:08.403
That's his whim, he doesn't wear them.

17:08.528 --> 17:11.114
-People talk, but...
-Are you defending him?

17:11.448 --> 17:12.490
Will you deny it?

17:13.950 --> 17:15.326
You know I'm right.

17:17.829 --> 17:20.123
<i>My name is Diego Armando, like you,</i>

17:20.206 --> 17:25.253
<i>and like many other Neapolitan boys</i>
<i>who were born while you were playing here.</i>

17:25.712 --> 17:28.465
<i>But, among all of those Diego Armandos,</i>

17:28.840 --> 17:32.343
<i>I'm the only one</i>
<i>whose surname is Maradona.</i>

17:32.677 --> 17:37.098
<i>My family tells me I rooted for Argentina</i>
<i>in the 1990 World Cup</i>

17:37.182 --> 17:39.184
<i>when I was only four,</i>

17:39.267 --> 17:42.145
<i>without knowing you were my dad.</i>

17:42.228 --> 17:45.690
<i>So it seems</i>
<i>I carry a piece of your heart in mine.</i>

17:45.815 --> 17:47.901
<i>The only thing is,</i>

17:47.984 --> 17:51.029
<i>please don't get mad,</i>
<i>but my favorite Argentinian team</i>

17:51.112 --> 17:52.655
<i>is River, your main rival.</i>

17:56.117 --> 17:57.744
<i>I wasn't able to meet you,</i>

17:57.827 --> 18:01.039
<i>but being your son makes me very proud,</i>

18:01.122 --> 18:03.833
<i>even if, at times,</i>
<i>people don't believe it.</i>

18:05.043 --> 18:06.669
<i>The rest of the time,</i>

18:06.753 --> 18:09.005
<i>people know me</i>

18:09.088 --> 18:11.633
<i>and look at me</i>
<i>to see if I am left-footed too.</i>

18:12.008 --> 18:15.220
<i>They are disappointed</i>
<i>when they find out that I am not.</i>

18:16.054 --> 18:19.140
<i>Anyway, they say I am a good player.</i>

18:19.224 --> 18:23.019
<i>Not as good as my dad, of course.</i>
<i>I am only human.</i>

18:23.102 --> 18:25.355
<i>You are considered a god.</i>

18:26.606 --> 18:28.858
<i>I hope you can answer my letter.</i>

18:29.150 --> 18:32.237
<i>I'd love to know something about you</i>

18:32.320 --> 18:34.447
<i>that doesn't come from newspapers or TV.</i>

18:34.531 --> 18:38.076
<i>Hugs. Hoping to be able</i>
<i>to get to know you soon.</i>

19:02.016 --> 19:03.726
How do I get to the World Cup?

19:03.810 --> 19:05.895
You have the best physical trainer.

19:06.896 --> 19:11.067
Listen, Diego.
There's an Italian cyclist called Moser

19:11.568 --> 19:13.653
who has just broken a record in Mexico.

19:13.778 --> 19:16.573
Something unreal
for an athlete used to cool climates.

19:16.656 --> 19:19.534
-Let's find out how he did it.
-I already did.

19:20.410 --> 19:23.496
The doctor who trained him
has a training center in Rome.

19:23.580 --> 19:25.164
-Shall I call him?
-Yes.

19:25.790 --> 19:28.126
But tell the guy not to say anything.

19:28.751 --> 19:32.046
If those stupid journalists find out,
and you know them,

19:32.630 --> 19:36.342
they'll say Maradona's mind is
on the World Cup, not on Napoli.

19:36.718 --> 19:37.719
Don't worry, Diego.

19:39.095 --> 19:41.347
Napoli is not playing for anything, right?

19:41.431 --> 19:45.894
That's why I don't care.
My mind set on the World Cup.

19:46.644 --> 19:49.397
You know how this works,
you have to save face.

19:49.480 --> 19:50.690
Okay, go, continue.

19:51.816 --> 19:52.734
Under.

20:40.406 --> 20:43.493
-Goal!
-Goal!

20:52.293 --> 20:54.671
<i>Napoli have now</i>
<i>gone four games without a win.</i>

20:54.754 --> 20:58.424
People say you are only
thinking about the World Cup.

20:58.508 --> 20:59.509
What people?

20:59.592 --> 21:03.054
Your neighbor, your sister, your mother?

21:03.137 --> 21:06.849
Losing and winning
are both part of the game.

21:06.975 --> 21:10.269
And besides,
Napoli is more than just Diego Maradona.

21:10.353 --> 21:13.982
But what is more important to you,
the World Cup or Napoli?

21:14.482 --> 21:17.944
The two things are connected.

21:18.027 --> 21:23.074
To do good there,
I need to give it all here, in Napoli.

21:23.366 --> 21:27.578
And I want to ask the Argentines
to stop attacking Bilardo,

21:27.829 --> 21:29.706
and the national team players.

21:29.956 --> 21:33.418
They believe all the bullshit they hear,
and those are lies

21:33.668 --> 21:37.380
to create conflict,
and we players are all on the same boat.

21:37.588 --> 21:40.425
So your relationship
with Passarella isn't worse?

21:41.217 --> 21:44.554
Please, I really admire Passarella.

21:44.721 --> 21:48.182
He's a world champion,
he gave us the qualification for Mexico.

21:48.349 --> 21:51.102
Come on, guys. Please, be serious.

21:54.313 --> 21:57.984
She arrives, spectacular as always.

21:58.693 --> 22:01.446
-And I recognize her from TV.
-Yes.

22:02.071 --> 22:05.950
So, I approach the owner of the club,
a friend of mine,

22:06.743 --> 22:10.246
and ask him, I sometimes have,
if she has a boyfriend.

22:10.371 --> 22:13.041
-I was single.
-And what does he say?

22:14.125 --> 22:19.297
-That Yayita had asked about me too.
-That's a lie! I didn't!

22:19.672 --> 22:22.175
Let me be a playboy!

22:22.300 --> 22:25.136
-Okay, say whatever you want.
-Just once!

22:25.219 --> 22:29.599
Well, I approach her, we go to the bar,
have a drink, loosen up,

22:29.766 --> 22:34.187
we start making out, and I,
the anxious one,

22:34.312 --> 22:38.316
start thinking which is
the best motel near the club.

22:39.817 --> 22:41.069
-Guille.
-Listen.

22:41.360 --> 22:46.657
Right at that moment, they call me
to tell me my best friend's dad died.

22:46.783 --> 22:48.910
I swear it happened.

22:49.160 --> 22:50.661
-I swear.
-It's true.

22:51.496 --> 22:52.413
I swear.

22:52.622 --> 22:56.459
I tell Yayita, "Look, I want you to know
something from here on out."

22:56.584 --> 23:00.004
-Yes.
-"To me, friends are everything."

23:01.297 --> 23:02.924
He did. I loved it.

23:03.007 --> 23:04.967
"You should know that.

23:05.301 --> 23:07.470
So, I have to go to a wake."

23:07.553 --> 23:09.889
-And what did she say?
-"I'll go with you."

23:10.098 --> 23:14.060
-What could I say?
-Since she was wearing a golden miniskirt.

23:14.143 --> 23:15.853
You remember the color, baby!

23:16.020 --> 23:19.190
-I took her home to change.
-Nothing happened there!

23:19.273 --> 23:22.360
-We went to the wake.
-I was very respectful, right?

23:22.485 --> 23:24.946
-I was wearing black.
-You were serene.

23:25.196 --> 23:26.531
You were serene.

