48:31.117 --> 48:34.537
<i>Now we see Napoli pushing, pushing hard.</i>

48:34.621 --> 48:37.665
<i>We go forward, the player Giordano.</i>
<i>Giordano. Goal!</i>

48:37.790 --> 48:41.002
<i>One to zero for Napoli on Sampdoria.</i>

48:41.127 --> 48:43.254
<i>The whole stadium celebrates the team.</i>

48:43.338 --> 48:45.715
<i>Here comes Maradona, an assist,</i>

48:45.798 --> 48:49.385
<i>Giordano's second goal,</i>
<i>he runs under the curve.</i>

48:49.469 --> 48:52.513
<i>All the San Paolo Stadium</i>
<i>in Naples unleashes.</i>

49:53.658 --> 49:54.701
Angelito.

49:55.284 --> 49:56.411
Come here, Diego.

49:58.204 --> 50:02.417
I promised you the shirt for
your grandson, but they took it from me.

50:02.583 --> 50:03.751
It doesn't matter.

50:03.960 --> 50:06.921
I'll buy him a random jersey
and tell him it's yours.

50:08.005 --> 50:09.882
-How are you?
-Same as always.

50:11.634 --> 50:13.720
I'm praying to God Almighty, Diego.

50:14.303 --> 50:18.391
I light a candle to San Gennaro
to have Argentina win the World Cup.

50:18.891 --> 50:20.685
If they hear you, they'll kill you.

50:20.768 --> 50:23.229
Why? I only support friends.

50:24.313 --> 50:26.357
Go Argentina.

50:26.941 --> 50:30.319
Go Argentina!

50:30.611 --> 50:33.239
See? Nothing happened.

50:35.408 --> 50:36.451
What about you?

50:37.827 --> 50:39.579
Good. Good.

50:41.581 --> 50:42.707
I don't know,

50:43.040 --> 50:44.333
I see you are sad.

50:48.463 --> 50:50.798
You didn't insult the referee today.

50:51.507 --> 50:53.468
You didn't stick your tongue out.

50:53.551 --> 50:56.095
You didn't fight
with any of the opposition.

50:57.847 --> 50:59.932
And that means I'm sad?

51:00.808 --> 51:01.726
Yes.

51:02.393 --> 51:04.061
You have to be okay, Diego.

51:06.063 --> 51:10.693
Hey. The last thing you need is
to fall apart just before your World Cup.

51:12.945 --> 51:15.239
-My World Cup?
-Yes, Diego.

51:15.907 --> 51:17.617
This will be your world cup.

51:17.700 --> 51:21.412
Otherwise, what was the point of
having them in Mexico, so high up.

51:21.496 --> 51:23.122
To make you shine,

51:23.206 --> 51:25.458
so that the defense cannot get to you.

51:25.541 --> 51:26.793
Listen to me,

51:26.876 --> 51:30.338
this will be a world cup
without man-to-man marking.

51:30.421 --> 51:31.839
Remember these words.

51:32.590 --> 51:35.134
So now you need to be happy.

51:36.427 --> 51:39.180
-What is being happy?
-What?

51:40.056 --> 51:42.308
You don't know what happiness is?

51:43.601 --> 51:45.228
Diego, what are you saying?

51:46.771 --> 51:47.980
Don't make me laugh.

51:49.315 --> 51:52.193
What about the night you snuck in here
with that girl?

51:52.276 --> 51:54.028
You think I was sleeping?

51:54.111 --> 51:57.865
What is that, if not happiness?

51:59.826 --> 52:01.202
The golden boy.

52:03.204 --> 52:04.956
Maradona is better than Pelé.

52:06.958 --> 52:09.210
And you don't know what happiness is.

52:10.837 --> 52:12.672
Maradona is better than Pelé.

53:11.439 --> 53:12.481
Are you ready?

53:13.524 --> 53:15.568
-Yes.
-I'll miss you a lot.

53:18.613 --> 53:21.073
Don't worry,
they say I'll be back first round.

53:21.157 --> 53:22.450
I hope not.

53:23.784 --> 53:27.288
I'd rather miss you, but you stay
until the last day of the Cup.

53:29.498 --> 53:30.750
-I love you.
-Me too.

53:32.710 --> 53:33.878
Change that face.

53:34.629 --> 53:36.881
-Should I carry this one?
-Okay.

54:12.667 --> 54:16.420
We'll talk every day.
If anything comes up,

54:16.587 --> 54:18.464
let me know, I'll solve it.

54:21.425 --> 54:22.551
Great.

54:28.474 --> 54:31.227
Stefano, take a right,
I have to go somewhere.

55:02.216 --> 55:05.011
-Don't you have to be in Mexico?
-I'm on my way.

55:06.679 --> 55:08.305
So what are you doing here?

55:09.974 --> 55:11.851
I treated you badly last time.

55:12.435 --> 55:13.811
I am sorry about that.

55:14.979 --> 55:17.940
I've been thinking a lot
about the three of us.

55:19.734 --> 55:21.652
Did you think of something new?

55:23.112 --> 55:24.238
No, the same.

55:25.281 --> 55:27.992
Leave then.
I haven't changed my mind either.

55:32.413 --> 55:34.331
Cristiana, go in the other room.

55:35.624 --> 55:36.959
Why did you come here?

55:38.669 --> 55:40.087
Why did you come here?

55:42.423 --> 55:43.799
We are humble people,

55:45.176 --> 55:46.969
but we have our dignity.

55:47.762 --> 55:48.721
Goodbye.

56:01.525 --> 56:05.988
RAI's special program "The truth about
Cristiana Sinagra's Pregnancy"

56:06.072 --> 56:10.493
was not broadcast at the time,
due to a request from Diego Maradona.

56:10.618 --> 56:14.080
The ban was carried out by
his influential Italian friends.

56:14.914 --> 56:18.417
Diego Junior, like his father,
played soccer professionally.

56:18.501 --> 56:22.088
He played in Napoli's youth teams
and the U-17 national team.

56:22.171 --> 56:25.758
Maradona publicly recognized him
as his son in 2016 at age 29.

56:26.425 --> 56:28.094
Since his time in Cebollitas,

56:28.177 --> 56:31.972
Maradona required regular injections
to be able to continue to play.

56:32.056 --> 56:34.475
In 2019, a prosthesis
was placed in his knee.

57:09.885 --> 57:12.471
<i>I don't have cops, I have...</i>

57:12.555 --> 57:17.226
<i>I have two men, two cops</i>
<i>that make room for me to go to trainings.</i>

57:17.309 --> 57:20.437
But they don't use any weapons.

57:20.521 --> 57:22.523
They don't hurt people.

58:57.743 --> 58:58.869
Stop!
